name: S&P/ASX 200 A-REIT OPIC
summary: The S&P/ASX 200 A-REIT OPIC is designed to measure the performance of Australian Real Estate Investment Trusts (A-REITs) within the S&P/ASX 200. It provides exposure to the listed property sector in Australia.

name: S&P/ASX 200 A-REIT
summary: The S&P/ASX 200 A-REIT is a sector-specific index representing the performance of Australian Real Estate Investment Trusts (A-REITs) within the S&P/ASX 200. It tracks the market capitalization-weighted performance of these A-REITs. The index provides insight into the performance of the Australian listed property sector.
